{"tid":711430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國消委會報告：深圳益力多優於香港益力多","createTime":"2018-06-21T13:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:34:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":158,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb43f121dcdedc8ac06020076446e75590d406b","tid":711430,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180621/s00004/57bbfb1eaa2a4a5130b7699fa09f5b69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180621%2Fs00004%2F57bbfb1eaa2a4a5130b7699fa09f5b69.jpg&h=18028c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳市消委會周二（19日）發表《2018年含乳飲料比較試驗報告》，當中提及深圳益力多活性乳酸菌和蛋白質的數量，均優於香港益力多，售價也低於香港。<br />\n<br />\n報告測試20款乳酸飲品，其中深圳採購16款，香港採購4款，所有樣本均符合國家要求。當中，報告將樣本分成三等，分別是「五星」、「四星」和「三星」。「五星」方面香港有2款入選，分別是產自蒙牛和明治。<br />\n<br />\n至於深受兩地人們歡迎的原味益力多，深圳出售的列「四星」，香港出售的則列「三星」。報告指，深圳益力多乳酸菌含量較香港多4.7倍，蛋白質含量則略高於香港6.25%。至於價錢，香港售價為2.3元人民幣一瓶，內地則為2.2元人民幣一瓶，相差4.55%。<br />\n<br />\n報告又特地提及，研究員在上水採購樣本時，發現便利店和藥房都堆起「益力多牆」。報告強調：「如果不能保證全程冷鏈的話，乳酸菌在運輸和保藏過程中就會老化死亡，活菌數量迅速下降。而且活性乳酸菌飲料在生產時，一般不需要經過高溫殺菌的，低溫也是抑制了有害微生物的生長。」"},{"pid":"1dd883afc89e98aad2f38b010923bc502fab4739","tid":711430,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sz315.org/index.php?m=content&amp;c=index&amp;a=show&amp;catid=6&amp;id=7997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsz315.org%2Findex.php%3Fm%3Dcontent%26c%3Dindex%26a%3Dshow%26catid%3D6%26id%3D7997&d=rKuEXMB5T1WbgDAVYwUu1dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2243e149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sz315.org/index.php?m=content&amp;c=index&amp;a=show&amp;catid=6&amp;id=7997</a>"},{"pid":"f870168ef86001fc57af778becd7728c65022138","tid":711430,"uid":38651,"like":125,"dislike":3,"score":122,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"比你飲都咪撚飲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港個啲係益生菌 <br />\n大陸個啲就唔知係咩菌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20deb4c424d6fb1b9ca03df1083b105396825961","tid":711430,"uid":59695,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔報香港益力多有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10d3e07f33091868526d0f20c00b836bfc0eb44","tid":711430,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"係啦, 支那狗唔買就對"},{"pid":"5a5d5a19be255b12b053e0ec84ec4e9a81f20786","tid":711430,"uid":73619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"可信度？"},{"pid":"c42481de237dbb1c2775f5b59ca9cffb8179ce97","tid":711430,"uid":87573,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"是但啦，正體字同大埔出產就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6172a64da186fa636eff8c03facb9caab3ffaf2b","tid":711430,"uid":126221,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"5a5d5a19be255b12b053e0ec84ec4e9a81f20786","tid":711430,"uid":73619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"可信度？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"1000% 可信！<br />\n<br />\n最緊要比 d 大陸人知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e496d67d9254f8630d8f83088e96be66484f1e8","tid":711430,"uid":68097,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"至於你信不信，我反正信了"},{"pid":"c47769bf550f66ffeaf5246b453e6fa846c57a62","tid":711430,"uid":26071,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"點解深圳依家超越香港 仲要特登落來香港採購<br />\n仲要評明治五星 擺明要做漢奸 快d雙規深圳消委會d官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027c003e8736b2f78749f90a7aaad4cb164156b0","tid":711430,"uid":31237,"like":9